        <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-responsive" src="~/css/images/plants/Weeds_Creeping_Knapweed1.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7" style="margin-top:-5%;">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Control and Report. <span class="text-muted">See for yourself.</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">
                <b>Caution: Please do not attempt to treat or dispose of Black Knapweed yourself. The department will treat, remove and dispose of alligator weed safely, at no cost to the land owner.</b>
                <br />If you suspect you may have seen Black Knapweed, please contact DEDJTR immediately. Phone 136 186, send an email to weed.spotters@ecodev.vic.gov.au using the our template here or make an online report here so that we can help you with most recent sightings.
                <br /><b>
                    or simply, report it from us:
